Well reading all this comments, it may be hard for some people to figure out the way to do it so i'm trying to make it easier by writing the fats way to reatch the goal.

1- creat a folder in C harddrive and call it "tomtom". make sure you creat it on the root of C.
2- copy the crack program called TT6_kg_4_C4pda.exe  and the map.mid that you what to crack !!. map is the name of the country map that you what to crack like "Eastern_Europe.mid"
3- Start the MS-Dos command line and get to the tomtom folder that you have  created on C by writing this on the command line.
cd c:\tomtom and then enter "cd is a dos command that stands for change dirrectory"
c:\tomtom>TT6_kg_4_C4pda.exe Eastern_Europe.mid  enter
Enter Device ID:
Now you should enter the device id the tomtom gives you when you choose manual activation.

4- after entering the device id you will get the code needed to activate the maps the tomtom. 

that's all.

If you what to activate more maps then just copy the map_name.mid to the tomtom folder that you have already created in C and follow the same procedure.

see u.

Here is some simple Steps for all the "Dummies"


1.Unrar, then u copy all the files (The whole map) on to your SD-card slot. on ur pocket pc:=)

2. Now u must install TomTom, The install should start automaticly...if not! u tap Autorun.exe...
When The install wants u to Enter a Serial u cancel the whole install.

3. Now u Copy the TomTom Navigator.exe and paste it where the Tom Tom has been installed.. when the warning about that it is allready another TomTom Navigator.exe there u just enter yes to copy! allright..
